longBusinessSummary: SOZAP AB (publ), a digital entertainment company, develops and distributes mobile games. The company offers mobile games, such as ARMED HEIST, Fishing Tour, and Questopia. SOZAP AB (publ) was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Nyköping, Sweden.
